review_blob: creamy, full body, lively, long finish, caramel, chocolate, floral, herbs, raisin, good balance between body, bitterness and acidity. Does have a very creamy mouthfeel with an aftertaste of milk chocolate.

Pours a big orange/brown head. Aromas of pear, raisins, citrus and herbs, quite bitter flavour, thinking of almond and pear. creamy texture. Drying mouthfeel afterwards. Flavours are too closed for me, having a hard time getting much out of it.
Aroma: cereal, citrus, yoghurt,  vanilla, stonefruit. Color: Golden. Liquid: cloudy, sparkling.medium sweetness, medium bitterness, heavily sour, medium body, ,
